.. actex:: BPU_Convert_KM_Miles
   :author: Jane Weyant
   :difficulty: 0
   :basecourse: fopp
   :topic: SimplePythonData/Exercises
   :from_source: F

   Write a program that will convert from kilometers into miles.  Prompt the user to enter a value of kilometers. 
   Print out a message with the corresponding number of miles.  (It may be helpful to know that 1 inch = 2.54 cm)
   ~~~~